{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/motorcycle-trainer-fees.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/motorcycle-trainer-fees","title":"Motorcycle trainer fees","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:12:36+00:00","details":{"need_id":"B143","business_proposition":true,"description":"Fees for becoming one of the different types a motorcycle trainer and registering with the Driving Standards Agency (DSA)","language":"en","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>There’s no charge to take the compulsory basic training (<abbr title=\"Compulsory basic training\">CBT</abbr>) and direct access scheme (<abbr title=\"Direct access scheme\">DAS</abbr>) instructor assessments, but there are fees for other types of motorcycle trainer tests and registration.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Driving Standards Agency (<abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr>) special test fee</h2>\n\n<p>As a fully qualified motorcycle trainer you can take the <a href=\"/dsa-special-tests-for-instructors\" title=\"DSA special test\"><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> special test</a> if you want your skills tested to the highest standard.</p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Fee type</th>\n      <th>Price</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> motorcycle special test</td>\n      <td>£163</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Register of post-test motorcycle trainers (<abbr title=\"Register of post-test motorcycle trainers\">RPMT</abbr>) fees</h2>\n\n<p>You have to pay a fee to take the qualifying tests and then register to <a href=\"/register-post-test-motorcycle-trainers-rpmt\" title=\"Join the RPMT\">join the <abbr title=\"Register of post-test motorcycle trainers\">RPMT</abbr></a> so you can give <a href=\"enhanced-rider-scheme/overview\" title=\"Enhanced rider scheme\">enhanced rider scheme</a> training. </p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Fee type</th>\n      <th>Price</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Starter pack</td>\n      <td>£6.99</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Theory and hazard perception test</td>\n      <td>£66</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Riding ability test</td>\n      <td>£114</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Instructional ability test</td>\n      <td>£114</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Registration and renewal fee (1 year)</td>\n      <td>£90</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Registration and renewal fee (4 years)</td>\n      <td>£240</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You have to pay the full amount again if you don’t pass any of the tests, and want to take another one.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>There are different <a href=\"http://www.nidirect.gov.uk/index/information-and-services/motoring/driving-for-a-living/how-do-i-become-an-approved-motorcycle-instructor-ami.htm\" title=\"Fees for motorcycle trainers\" rel=\"external\">fees for motorcycle trainers</a> in Northern Ireland.</p>\n</div>\n\n","alternative_title":""},"tags":[{"title":"Teaching people to drive","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/driving%2Fteaching-people-to-drive.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Becoming an instructor, applying for licences, booking tests and rules","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=driving%2Fteaching-people-to-drive","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving/teaching-people-to-drive"},"parent":{"title":"Driving, transport and travel","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/driving.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Book your driving test or get a tax disc online, find out the legal requirements for buying, owning, importing or scrapping a car or motorcycle, and read about your rights and responsibilities as a driver.","short_description":"","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=driving","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving"},"parent":null}},{"title":"Business Link","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/businesslink.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"short_description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=businesslink","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/businesslink"},"parent":null}],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/become-direct-access-scheme-motorcycle-instructor.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/become-direct-access-scheme-motorcycle-instructor","title":"Become a direct access scheme (DAS) motorcycle instructor","format":"guide","updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:18:21+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/become-dsa-assessed-cbt-motorcycle-instructor.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/become-dsa-assessed-cbt-motorcycle-instructor","title":"Become a DSA assessed CBT motorcycle instructor","format":"guide","updated_at":"2012-12-03T15:25:28+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/register-post-test-motorcycle-trainers-rpmt.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/register-post-test-motorcycle-trainers-rpmt","title":"Register of post-test motorcycle trainers (RPMT)","format":"guide","updated_at":"2012-11-07T14:52:39+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/set-up-run-motorcycle-approved-training-body-atb.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/set-up-run-motorcycle-approved-training-body-atb","title":"Set up and run a motorcycle approved training body (ATB)","format":"guide","updated_at":"2012-11-30T16:05:45+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/become-a-motorcycle-instructor.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/become-a-motorcycle-instructor","title":"Become a motorcycle instructor","format":"smart-answer","updated_at":"2012-11-30T14:11:43+00:00"}]}